@startuml
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F4F8
skinparam ArrowColor #333333
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #FFE6CC

title SD-11 - Library Statistics Flow

actor "Operator Perpustakaan" as User
participant Browser
participant Server
participant "Pendataan\nController" as Controller
database "MySQL" as Database

note over Browser
    loadChartData() dipanggil otomatis
    bersamaan dengan loadData()
    saat halaman rekap selesai dirender
end note

Browser -> Server: 1. AJAX GET /pendataan/get_chart_stats\n?tahun=...&nomor_pokok=...&date_from=...&date_to=...\nHeader: X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest
activate Server

Server -> Controller: 2. get_chart_stats()
activate Controller

alt Bukan AJAX request
    Controller -> Browser: 3a. HTTP 403\n{"error": "Forbidden"}
else AJAX request valid
    note right of Controller
        Sanitasi parameter via xss_clean():
        - tahun, nomor_pokok, date_from, date_to
    end note

    Controller -> Database: 3b. Cek file cache\nchart_stats_v2_{md5(filter)}
    activate Database
    Database --> Controller: 4. Cache miss
    deactivate Database

    note right of Controller
        Helper sum_q(id_pertanyaan):
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM(CAST(j.jawaban AS UNSIGNED)), 0)
        FROM jawaban_koleksi j
        JOIN identitas_input_koleksi i ON i.id_koleksi = j.id_koleksi
        WHERE j.id_pertanyaan = {id}
        AND j.jawaban REGEXP '^[0-9]+$'
        AND i.tahun_data = {tahun}
        [AND filter nomor_pokok, date_from, date_to]
    end note

    Controller -> Database: 5. Stat cards:\nCOUNT(*) FROM identitas_input_koleksi\nWHERE tahun_data = {tahun} [+ filter]
    activate Database
    Database --> Controller: 6. total_laporan
    deactivate Database

    Controller -> Database: 7. sum_q(15) → total judul tercetak\nsum_q(16) → total judul digital\nsum_q(51) → total anggota 2025
    activate Database
    Database --> Controller: 8. Return nilai agregasi
    deactivate Database

    Controller -> Database: 9. Chart 1 — Koleksi Saat Ini:\nsum_q(15) Judul Tercetak\nsum_q(17) Eksemplar Tercetak\nsum_q(16) Judul Digital\nsum_q(18) Eksemplar Digital
    activate Database
    Database --> Controller: 10. Return 4 nilai
    deactivate Database

    Controller -> Database: 11. Chart 2 — Pertumbuhan Koleksi:\n2025: sum_q(19,20,21,22)\n2026: sum_q(23,24,25,26)
    activate Database
    Database --> Controller: 12. Return 8 nilai (2 dataset × 4 label)
    deactivate Database

    Controller -> Database: 13. Chart 3 — Pengunjung & Akses:\n2025: sum_q(45) Onsite, sum_q(46) Online,\n      sum_q(49) Akses Teknologi\n2026: sum_q(47) Onsite, sum_q(48) Online,\n      sum_q(50) Akses Teknologi
    activate Database
    Database --> Controller: 14. Return 6 nilai (2 dataset × 3 label)
    deactivate Database

    Controller -> Database: 15. Chart 4 — Pemanfaatan Tercetak:\n2025: sum_q(31) Dibaca, sum_q(33) Dipinjam\n2026: sum_q(35) Dibaca, sum_q(37) Dipinjam
    activate Database
    Database --> Controller: 16. Return 4 nilai (2 dataset × 2 label)
    deactivate Database

    Controller -> Database: 17. Chart 5 — Distribusi Jenis Perpustakaan:\nSELECT j.jawaban AS nilai,\n  o.label_opsi AS label,\n  COUNT(*) AS total\nFROM jawaban_koleksi j\nJOIN identitas_input_koleksi i\n  ON i.id_koleksi = j.id_koleksi\nLEFT JOIN opsi_pertanyaan_koleksi o\n  ON o.id_pertanyaan = j.id_pertanyaan\n  AND o.nilai_opsi = j.jawaban\nWHERE j.id_pertanyaan = 4\nAND i.tahun_data = {tahun} [+ filter]\nGROUP BY j.jawaban\nORDER BY total DESC
    activate Database
    Database --> Controller: 18. Return distribusi jenis perpustakaan
    deactivate Database

    note right of Controller
        Simpan ke file cache
        Key: chart_stats_v2_{md5(filter)}
        TTL: 300 detik
    end note

    Controller -> Browser: 19. Return JSON:\n{\n  stat_cards: {total_laporan, judul_tercetak,\n               judul_digital, anggota_2025},\n  koleksi_saat_ini: {labels, data},\n  pertumbuhan: {labels, data_2025, data_2026},\n  pengunjung: {labels, data_2025, data_2026},\n  pemanfaatan: {labels, data_2025, data_2026},\n  distribusi_jenis: {labels, data}\n}
    deactivate Controller
    deactivate Server

    Browser -> User: 20. Update stat cards\nRender 5 chart via Chart.js 4.4.1:\n- Chart 1: horizontal bar (koleksi)\n- Chart 2: grouped bar (pertumbuhan)\n- Chart 3: grouped bar (pengunjung)\n- Chart 4: grouped bar (pemanfaatan)\n- Chart 5: donut + custom legend (jenis)
end

opt User mengubah filter
    User -> Browser: 21. Ubah filter → klik Filter
    Browser -> Server: 22. AJAX GET /pendataan/get_chart_stats\n(parameter filter baru)
    activate Server
    Server -> Controller: 23. get_chart_stats()
    activate Controller
    note right of Controller
        Proses identik langkah 3b-19
        dengan parameter filter baru.
        Cache key berbeda → miss → query ulang
    end note
    Controller -> Browser: 24. Return JSON data terfilter
    deactivate Controller
    deactivate Server
    Browser -> User: 25. Destroy & re-render semua chart\nUpdate stat cards
end

@enduml